! Collaborative Blog Plugin

This plugin transforms TiddlyWiki into a WordPress-style collaborative blog with a clean, professional interface.

!! Features

''Content & Publishing:''
* Clean blog layout with hidden wiki controls
* Multiple author support with attribution
* Featured posts and favorite articles
* Custom post types: Events, Galleries, Videos, Quotes
* Categories and tags for organization
* Post archive and table of contents
* Draft management
* Static pages support

''User Interface:''
* Left sidebar navigation with recently updated posts
* 5 professional themes (Historical, Modern, Dark, Vibrant, Professional)
* Enhanced search with filters (post type, category, author)
* Responsive design for mobile and desktop
* Discrete admin panel with post type selector

''Automatic Saving & Deployment:''
* Automatic GitHub saving via Cloudflare Functions (integrated)
* Password-protected saves with session management
* Save notifications and statistics
* Real-time deployment via Cloudflare Pages

''Analytics & Insights:''
* Privacy-friendly analytics (Plausible, Simple Analytics)
* Google Analytics (GA4) support
* Custom analytics provider support
* Easy Control Panel configuration

