!! Customization

''Site Identity:''
* Edit `$:/SiteTitle` and `$:/SiteSubtitle` to change site name

''Themes:''
* Choose from 5 built-in themes in Control Panel ‚Üí Appearance
* Edit `$:/plugins/collaborative-blog/theme-controller` to create custom themes
* Modify 40+ CSS variables for complete design control

''Navigation:''
* Edit `$:/plugins/collaborative-blog/Navigation` to customize menu links

''Advanced Styling:''
* Edit `$:/plugins/collaborative-blog/styles` for base styles and components
* All styles use CSS variables for easy theming

